Package com.fssa.librarymanagement.constants

Class BookConstants

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.librarymanagement.constants.BookConstants
public class BookConstants extends Object
This class holds constant values related to books in the library management system. It provides predefined values, Error Messages and Success messages.
